  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Diagnosis of androgenetic alopecia

          -  Fitzpatrick Skin types I-IV

          -  Ludwig I-4, II-1, II-2, or frontal

          -  Active hair loss within last 12 months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Photosensitivity to laser light

          -  Malignancy in the target area

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Lactating females
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
